### obtener todos los plots
GET http://localhost:3000/api/plots

### obtener un plot
GET http://localhost:3000/api/plots/684c8bd02ae4e5f0333939af

### crear un nuevo plot
POST http://localhost:3000/api/plots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lote experimental",
  "cadastralNumber": "CN-001",
  "area": 12.5,
  "location": "Sector norte",
  "status": "planted",
  "tasks": [
    {
      "type": "planting",
      "date": "2025-08-01T00:00:00.000Z",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "name": "Maíz híbrido",
          "type": "seed",
          "quantity": 50,
          "unit": "kg"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rainfall": [
    {
      "date": "2025-08-02T00:00:00.000Z",
      "millimeters": 12.3
    }
  ]
}

